{"tid":2462163,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"欠債張致恒老婆外家猛料 外公盧沃勤龍紋身始祖幫陳惠敏吳志雄操刀","createTime":"2021-03-25T23:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T03:34:07.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"94f9ed27237464fe703fb341e63654b0f1ea5ea1","tid":2462163,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:50:47.000Z","msg":"張致恒（Steven）前年與女粉絲雯雯奉子成婚，大仔出世不久，兩夫婦再生多細仔。Steven孭起一家四口的重擔外，更飼養了不少寵物，工作量不多，開支卻不少，但他全家並沒節儉起來，難怪不停向圈中好友借貸度日。 <br />\n<br />\n不過，原來雯雯外家大有來頭，外公盧沃勤是龍紋身始祖，不單止陳惠敏及吳志雄這些大哥找他紋身，連劉德華、張學友和謝霆鋒也曾找他操刀，而且他有不少江湖契仔契女！<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_779688_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_779688_0&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Gv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=1786e3eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_779688_0&h=61b60e7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_779688_0</a>"},{"pid":"cdbeab7648572c80d7558c3ee08b45de21694362","tid":2462163,"uid":130351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:01:58.000Z","msg":"劉德華、張學友和謝霆鋒<br />\n呢3個都有紋身嫁咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbb2eedf2379a84ccecdc683a1bb42da64a489b","tid":2462163,"uid":14130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdbeab7648572c80d7558c3ee08b45de21694362","tid":2462163,"uid":130351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:01:58.000Z","msg":"劉德華、張學友和謝霆鋒<br />\n呢3個都有紋身嫁咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:06:07.000Z","msg":"重睇"},{"pid":"471b03732d86c67f723913371837753de8e87510","tid":2462163,"uid":274432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:09:23.000Z","msg":"好撚煩呀呢一家垃圾"},{"pid":"61eddde01f02e37bb64eeefc3b70dcc8ca31322b","tid":2462163,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT